ing: 1 (8 ounce) container frozen whipped topping, thawed
des: "A quick and easy salad that is great for any occasion. This cool, shimmering treat makes a wonderful dessert, too."
ins: In a large bowl, mix the cherry pie filling, sweetened condensed milk, crushed pineapple and whipped topping. Chill in the refrigerator at least 2 hours before serving.
